'''Lola Curich''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]]. It contained the [[Allied Tion Historical Society]], [[Thorip Norr]], [[Fronde's Airspeeders]], the [[Astromech Heaven]] outlet, and [[PetVac]]. The [[Lona Cranith River]] separated Lola Curich from [[Lianna City]].
